resources.string:
This app is specially made for SIT students.

Slide sliders to select quiz marks

No average is done between quiz 2 and 3 while adding credits

For test credit calculation .34 is the multiplier used

Ex. 17/.34=50 so if your get 28 marks then
your credits are 28X .34=9.52 ~ 10 credits
